            <thetext>Created attachment 825
Patch to add event key

The &quot;readOnly&quot; property of qx.ui.form.AbstractField is missing the &quot;change&quot; key, thus not firing a &quot;changeReadOnly&quot; event when the property changes. However, to make the readOnly property bindable, this event is needed.

A patch is attached.</thetext>
